haReport:
This mission was flown by:
Kmdr Patrik Schorner
Ltn Detlef Schwarzer

 The mission was flown from Balatre aerodrome.

Successes include the following: 
On 07/10/1916 near Courcy.
A Sopwith Strutter of Esc 227 was brought down by Urs Kehlmann of Jasta 16b.
Cne Felix Desmoulinais was killed in action.
S/Lt Emile Hereau was killed in action.
Urs Kehlmann was  flying a Albatros D.II.

On 07/10/1916 near Baleycourt.
A F.E.2b of Esc 13 was brought down by Rudiger Bretschneider of Jasta 16b.
Cne Theophile Declais was killed in action.
S/Lt Charles-Henri Robert was killed in action.
Rudiger Bretschneider was  flying a Albatros D.II.
